Title:cc_putchar
Subject:Recreate the putchar function, you will print a character on the standard output (stdout).
Allowed_functions:write
Files_to_turn_in:cc_putchar.c
Prototype:int putchar(int c);
Hints:$> man putchar
Examples:$> a, $> b, $> c
Code: int putchar(int c) { write(STDOUT_FILENO, &c, 1); return(0); }